| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[i_item_sk@0 as i_item_sk, i_item_desc@1 as i_item_desc, round(vector_search().score,Int64(1))@2 as round(vector_search().score,Int64(1))]   |
|               |   SortPreservingMergeExec: [score@3 DESC], fetch=4                                                                                                                |
