|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[i_item_sk@0 as i_item_sk, i_item_desc@1 as i_item_desc, round(score@2, 1) as round(vector_search().score,Int64(1)), score@2 as score] |
|               |         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                        |
|               |           CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                             |
|               |             FilterExec: i_item_sk@0 > 5                                                                                                                           |
|               |               ProjectionExec: expr=[i_item_sk@0 as i_item_sk, i_item_desc@2 as i_item_desc, score@1 as score]                                                     |
|               |                 CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                       |
|               |                   CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                     |
|               |                     HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Left, on=[(i_item_sk@0, i_item_sk@0)], projection=[i_item_sk@0, score@1, i_item_desc@3]             |
|               |                       CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                 |
|               |                         RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([i_item_sk@0], 3), input_partitions=3                                                                  |
|               |                           CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                             |
|               |                             ProjectionExec: expr=[CAST(key@0 AS Int32) as i_item_sk, 1 - distance@1 as score]                                                     |
|               |                               RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                |
|               |                                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                |
|               |                                   S3VectorsQueryExec: limit=100                                                                                                   |
|               |                       CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                 |
